== But it should be nice! ==

By~the~way we would like to notice that Luwrain does not want to~be~an~ordinary project.
We have~to~do~everything possible to~make it~intriguing and attractive.
In~pursuit of~that aim any~ideas  how~to~improve user impressions,
how~to~make usage easier 
or how~to~eliminate one more boring and time consuming thing 
would be definitely appreciated here.
If Luwrain consumers once  would be~able to fill themselves  using 
something that actually is not a~accessibility technology,
we could treat this moment as~a~real success 
making Luwrain itself very close to a~state of~the~art.

Luwrain is rather specific  in~this sense as~it has such intention 
being not a~commercial product 
and that has corresponding explanation:
commercial companies  always are not free from the~one serious problem:
all products they  originate usually die at~the~moment of their fault
or at~the moment when their products do not yield gain any more.
It is a~really serious problem because with~these circumstances 
a~lot of users can be left without a~tool they really need.

== Research part ==

Another important part of~Luwrain idea is an~acceptance of~results 
given by~modern scientific research in~relevant areas.
The~world of~information technologies is not frozen,
it~changes permanently  and Luwrain should reflect that properly.
Thus everybody can fill himself completely free to~propose new ideas 
if that does not violate ten terms stated above.

